1015
01:26:19,886 --> 01:26:22,366
Sve se dogodilo u
ulici Marlinton...

1016
01:26:28,943 --> 01:26:31,836
- Bennett.
- Moramo prekinuti odmah.

1017
01:26:31,837 --> 01:26:33,761
Ne smemo rizikovati više
ubistvom Toma Cravena.

1018
01:26:34,119 --> 01:26:35,598
Prekasno je.

1019
01:26:35,879 --> 01:26:37,728
To je već učinjeno.

1020
01:26:59,779 --> 01:27:01,242
